      "body": {
        "en": "Visual inspection is the first line of quality verification:\n\n1. Surface Defects: Check for cracks, seams, laps, or burrs\n2. Head Defects: Verify proper head formation, no flash or fins\n3. Thread Defects: Check for torn threads, stripped threads, or die lines\n4. Coating Quality: Verify uniform coating, no bare spots or peeling\n5. Marking Verification: Confirm grade marking matches specifications\n6. Packaging: Check for proper labeling and moisture protection\n\nUse 10x magnification for detailed thread inspection.",
